rComments: Professeur Boreux est mon prof préféré à date! Il y a plusieurs travuax mais tous les instructions sont précises et il est toujours disponible pour répondre aux questions. On peut voir que le prof se soucie du bien-être des étudiants et est très considérables. Cela fait déjà 4 cours que je prends avec lui et j'espère en prendre d'autre.

UOttawa is very lucky to have this gem of a professor. Professor Boreux genuinely cares about his students and shows an interest in getting to know each of his students on an individual level. His presentations are clear & concise. Keeps us engaged in class with polls. We even got to annotate the zoom screen with our contributions, etc. Amazing.

This is my first time taking a class with prof. Boreux. Excellent prof and an even better person, he really cares about his students and shared mental health ressources during Covid times . Homework is lengthy but no final exam. He knows his material although he speaks quickly, if French isnt your first language it might be difficult. (Worth it)
Great prof! Really passionate about what he teachers and cares about his students. He made online classes a lot more enjoyable by doing polls, breakout rooms, annotations on Zoom, etc.

Great prof, you could tell he really cared about his students and their learning! His marking was very straightforward and assignments were clear in what you had to do. His lectures were slightly dry but don't let that deter you because he explained everything really well!

Dr. Max is a great prof. Took his geomorphology class at MTA. Notes are very descriptive and on point. Lots of material to learn. Very fair tests. Sometimes gives hints in class about exam material. Fair marker. Good teaching style. Understood all material easilly. AMAZING TEACHER OVERALL . Would be awesome if he stays at Mount Allison permanently

- Great Prof!  He has amazing lectures and describes the content very well.  His   notes contain more than enough information (textbook not needed) - Show up to class! He will tell you what to study for the tests - A lot of content.  If you dont like ecology dont take this class - Sometimes speaks too quickly - Labs are fun but reports are long
